data.description: HEATED SALT-WATER POOL!! NO HOA!! 3 bed 2 bath home with a BONUS ROOM that could be converted into a 4th bedroom, over 1500 heated sqft with brand new custom tile flooring throughout the home and a custom master bath with a jacuzzi tub!! Detached shed!! DOUBLE DRIVEWAY, which also goes to the backyard, where you can park an RV, trailer, or boat and still have extra room. Come check it out quickly before it's gone. This property is located just 1 mile from a grocery store, gas station, and post office. Easy access to Highway 9, 31, and 22. Estimated about 15 minutes from the BEACH! Square footage is approximate and not guaranteed. Buyer responsible for verification.
